strings:
<voice_0x01001C63><se_high>Princess Medea: Thank you, <hero>.
Now we can talk again!
<voice_0x01001C64><se_high>Princess Medea: I've been wanting to talk to you about my fiancé. His name is Prince Charmles.
<voice_0x01001C65><se_high>Princess Medea: Our marriage was decided long ago, even before my grandmother died. It's some kind of arrangement between our families.

<voice_0x01001C66><se_high>Princess Medea: But I've never even met him.
I wonder what kind of person he is?
<voice_0x01001C67><se_high>Princess Medea: I hope he's someone like you, <hero>...

<voice_0x01001C68><se_high>Princess Medea: Oh! I can feel the spring water wearing off...
Let's talk again soon!
